ect 'org.apache.groovy.groovy-templates_tests'.\n61:mergeNativeTraceMetadata - Merges runtime metadata trace output directories with native-image-utils generate\n68:generateDynamicAccessReport - Builds native tests with dynamic-access tracking and reuses Gradle up-to-date checks when inputs and classpath are unchanged\n69:jacocoTestCoverageVerification - Verifies code coverage metrics based on specified rules for the test task.\n70:jacocoTestReport - Generates code coverage report for the test task.\n71:listLibraryJars - Lists resolved JARs for the tested library (one per line)\n72:nativeTest - Executes the test native binary\n73:runNativeTraceImage - Runs the trace-enabled test native image once and writes runtime metadata trace output\n74:test - Runs the test suite.\n79:checkstyleTest - Run Checkstyle analysis for test classes\n82:compileTestGroovy - Compiles the test Groovy source.\n83:compileTestJava - Compiles test Java source.\n90:nativeTestBuild\n91:nativeTestCompileClasspathJar - Builds a pathing jar for the test native binary\n94:processTestResources - Processes test resources.\n101:[Incubating] Problems report is available at: file:///home/vjovanov/c/forge/forge8/graalvm-reachability-metadata/forge/local_repositories/forge_worktrees/2468-4e28ecc8/tests/src/org.apache.groovy/groovy-templates/4.0.24/build/reports/problems/problems-report.html\n","exit_code":0,"status":"completed"}}
